::Zardus::

Zardus looks back at Battera as he flies, wondering how Feline had recruited 
her. He turns his head back forward, the battle in sight. There would be more 
time for that later, for now he had bots to slagg. "Here they are. Kill 
everyone that doesn't register as an Alliance member."

Flying into the battle and near to Oblitertron, Zardus opened fire, shooting 
his plasma launcher at Astral.
